review_text: Pathways and cycling lanes makes this park a must see in nearby Lachine. With views of the St Lawrence River and the historic canals, i recently spent some time photographing its' character using a modified camera. Whether you come for exercise or relaxation, the Park has many amenities and is accompanied by exceptional views.

The park is amazing. Has outstanding view to the river. You can watch the beautiful sunset. You are free to barbecue and have fun with your family. It is a good place for ridding bicycle, exercising, running, playing skate and etc. It is one of my favourite place to visit.

Big and open park which is great as it’s not accesible by car, only walking or by bike.

It’s a great bike path around the island and river family friendly.

Not too many outdoor park games for kids
